dct_description_sm: Relief is shown by hachures. Map shows international, intercolonial and district boundaries, railways, and roads. Towns, rivers, and major points of elevation also marked. "Land Survey & Mines Department T.T. 21. 1. 24." "The area marked 'A' shews the provinces of Ruanda & Urundi & the boundary as defined by Art. 7 of the Mandate & the Milner-Orts agreement. The area marked 'B' shews the modification approved by the League of Nations in 1923." "306. WT 2397 A./1253. 875. 5. 24." Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, map reproduction is attached to companion volume.
